    <h1> Brazilians snacks </h1>
    <h2> A Mix of Sweet & Savory </h2>
<p>Brazilian cuisine is a rich blend of indigenous, African, Portuguese, and immigrant influences,  creating a diverse and flavorful food culture. <br/> Each region of Brazil has its own specialties based on local ingredients and traditions.

</p>
   
